  "title": "Accountant",
  "description": "<p><strong>about the company</strong></p><p>Our client is a global investment management firm and a significant player within the real estate sector. </p><p><strong>about the job</strong></p><p>You will report to the Finance Manager and be part of a collaborative team of 2 managing the comprehensive accounting functions for a diverse portfolio of entities. In this role, you will be hands-on across the full spectrum of financial accounts, taking ownership of financial statements and management reporting. You will also be supporting the team in internal budget cycles as required.</p><p><strong>skills and experience required</strong></p><p>You will possess a Bachelor Degree in Accountancy or its equivalent and come with minimally 2 years of experience in a similar capacity. You will be an agile and grounded individual who thrives working in a fast-paced environment and a lean team structure. Prior experience in ERP improvement projects will be advantageous.</p><p>To apply online please use the 'apply' function, alternatively you may contact Francine. (EA: 94C3609/ R22104071)</p>",
